nodes.text: Star Wars: Build Your Own R2-D2 57

Star Wars: Build Your Own R2-D2 57 is the fifty-seventh issue of the Star Wars: Build Your Own R2-D2 published by De Agostini. Released in 2018, it came with the dome panel and left foot parts for the buildable R2-D2.
